# example-app cursor rules

Setup: run `pnpm install` before working on this repo.

Build: run `pnpm build` to produce a production bundle in `dist/`.

Test: run `pnpm test` before opening a PR. All tests must pass.

Code style:
- 2-space indentation
- Single quotes for strings
- Trailing commas in multi-line literals

Pull requests:
- Title format: Conventional Commits (feat:, fix:, chore:, etc.)
- One logical change per PR
- Link the related issue in the description

Security:
- Never commit .env files
- Run `pnpm audit` before publishing
